data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. WOW!  Talk about curb appeal.  This over 2700 sq. ft. single family home in Waterset is a show stopper.  Architectural detail to roof line and exterior stucco is exceptional.  The home has a wide formal entry way with a clear view to the back sliding glass doors. A total of 4 bedrooms, with one up front with bath and 2 additional just off the entryway sharing a bath. The oversized kitchen adjoins the family/dining area and includes stainless steel appliances with a 36" cooktop and wall oven/microwave.  The designer vent hood adds to the elegance of the 42" cabinets with crown molding atop beautiful granite countertops.  The kitchen/dining/family room become the focal point of the home with tons of natural light from the large windows and sliding glass doors that open onto the extended covered lanai.  Your owner retreat is the "star" of this fabulous home.  It is very large with double door entry and exquisite spa like bath which includes shower and garden tub, again lots of natural light.  And to top it off, the largest of our owners closets with double shelving. The den/office just off the entry way. This is the perfect home to enjoy your new lifestyle in Waterset.
